"par_id81630022708336\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <emph>No duplications</emph> option is case sensitive. Therefore, values \"A\" and \"a\" are each considered as unique values."
msgstr "L'opzione <emph>Nessun duplicato</emph> distingue tra maiuscole e minuscole. I valori \"A\" e \"a\" vengono dunque considerati valori univoci."

